<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Subscription Expiry Reminder</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f8f8f8;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .container {
      background-color: #ffffff;
      margin: 50px auto;
      padding: 20px;
      max-width: 600px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    }
    .header {
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #333333;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .content {
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #555555;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }
    .cta-button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      margin-top: 20px;
      background-color: #4CAF50;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 30px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #999999;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">Hi {{name}},</div>
    <div class="content">
      We wanted to remind you that your subscription will expire in <strong>{{daysLeft}} day{{#unless daysLeft==1}}s{{/unless}}</strong>.
      <br><br>
      To continue enjoying our services without interruption, please renew your subscription before it expires.
      <br><br>
      <a href="https://yourdomain.com/renew" class="cta-button">Renew Now</a>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      &copy; {{currentYear}} Your Company. All rights reserved.
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
